settings.description: This course includes the new SMB2 mushroom!
A remake of the first half of Donut Plains 3 from Super Mario World. I made this just to get a hang on what this editor can do. Level design credit goes to the original creators at Nintendo.
Still isn't a rip-off of a series called "The 8 worlds" This is water plains.
The first level of Super Mario Land 2: 6 Golden Coins.
Not a Rip-off of an existing series called "The 8 Worlds" I swear. This is the bunker part; you will see this again soon.
Not a Rip-off of an existing series called "The 8 Worlds" I swear. This is the Desert Lake; it goes straight to the deserts underground bunker.
Not a Rip-off of an existing series called "The 8 Worlds" I swear. This is desert plains, with a TON of coins to collect.
Not a Rip-off of an existing series called "The 8 Worlds" I swear. This is 1B, the underground pipe area part thing new area idea, what to name it tho?
Test some of your skills with the Tanooki Suit in this brief adventure up in the sky!
A short level that shows Mario saving all the dimensions from destruction.
Mario Falls down after taking on the airship he was on, he finds himself in this area, he will need to be careful and not die! Cloud Tower is next.
A short level that shows Mario getting past bowsers defenses to his castle, I wonder why it's so weak? Bowser's Castle is Next.
Mario finds himself in a World with water, can he escape to cloud land? Base of operations of M and L are ahead, so be quick!
Mario finds a rest area and stays there to pass some time before he's ready to fight bowser. It seems inside it is testing gizmos. Cloud Land 3 is next.
Mario Adventures Through the clouds to get to Bowsers Castle, nowhere near yet...
